parameters:
Ruth: (She hasn't noticed yet! Now, to quickly
drag her under the counter!)

Tia: "Lord Ruth, please command me to do
anything♥"

Ruth: (Heh heh heh... Now I'm ready to exploit the
female warrior's opening!)
Ruth: "A female warrior is staying here, right?"

Ruth: "Then, I'll sneak into her room tonight, and
I'll need your help with that."

Ruth: (Maybe I should use the medicine I got from
Cyan, just to be safe.)
There are still things to do
Ruth: "Alright, I'll contact you again later."
Tia: "Will you be waiting here until nightfall?"

Ruth: (Before that, I should use the medicine I
got from Cyan, just to be safe.)
Ruth: "Yes, but first mix this into his dinner."
There are still things to do

Ruth: "Then, I'll come back to check on you
later."
Riina: "Monster?! A monster, ohhh! Mama! Mamaaaa!"

Tia: "Riina-chan, what's wrong? There's no way
there's a monster..."

Innkeeper: "Even if Reeza-chan isn't here, I'll
protect this shop!"

events.name: 宿屋の親父カウンター内
